ŠŻśŠľçŠľîšÜäŠŐÇŠť»Šľçšźá https://www.panwenbin.cn/posts/mpv-play-web-video/ -<h2 id="ňąĹŠť║">ňąĹŠť║</h2>
<blockquote>
<p>LinuxńŞőšÜäChromeŠĺşŠöżŔžćÚóĹńŞŹŠö»ŠîüšíČń╗ÂňŐáÚÇčŃÇéŔÖŻšäÂFirefoxňĆ»ń╗ąŠö»Šîü´╝îńŻćŠś»ň╣│ŠŚÂŔ┐śŠś»šöĘChromeňĄÜńŞÇšé╣ŃÇéÚůŹšŻ«ŔžćÚóĹňť░ňŁÇŔžúŠ×ÉŠś»ňĆ»ń╗ąŔ«ęMPVŠŁąŠĺşŠöżšÜä´╝îŠşúňąŻmpvŔ┐śňćůšŻ«ń║ćŔ░âšöĘyt-dlpŠŁąňĄäšÉćŔžćÚóĹňť░ňŁÇŔžúŠ×É´╝îyoutubeňĺîBšźÖÚâŻŠö»Šîü´╝îÚéúŠşúňąŻŔ»ĽńŞÇńŞőňÉžŃÇé</p></blockquote>
<h2 id="ÚůŹšŻ«">ÚůŹšŻ«</h2>
<p>mpvň╝ÇňÉ»šíČń╗ÂňŐáÚÇčŃÇéň»╣ń║ÄIntelŠáŞň┐âŠśżňŹí´╝îÚůŹšŻ«Šľçń╗Â<code>~/.config/mpv/mpv.conf</code>ńŞşŠĚ╗ňŐáňŽéńŞőňćůň«╣´╝Ü</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#b0c4de;background-color:#282c34;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic"># ňÉ»šöĘšíČń╗ÂŔžúšáü</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#dcaeea">hwdec</span><span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span>vaapi
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic"># Šîçň«ÜŔžćÚóĹŔżôňç║ňÉÄšź»´╝łňĆ»ÚÇëň░ŁŔ»ĽńŞŹňÉîš╗äňÉł´╝ë</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#dcaeea">vo</span><span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span>gpu
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic"># ňĆ»ÚÇë´╝ÜÚĺłň»╣ŠčÉń║Ťňť║ŠÖ»ń╝śňîľ</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#dcaeea">profile</span><span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span>gpu-hq
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>ńŞőŔŻŻŠťÇŠľ░šëłŠťČšÜäyt-dlp´╝îňŤáńŞ║ŠŚžšëłňĆ»ŔâŻňĚ▓š╗ĆŠŚáŠĽłŃÇéŠłĹšŤ«ňëŹńŞőŔŻŻšÜäšëłŠťČŠś»<code>2025.02.19</code>´╝îŠöżňł░ń║ć<code>/usr/local/bin/</code>ńŞőŃÇé</p>
<p>Ŕ«żšŻ«yt-dlpšÜäÚůŹšŻ«Šľçń╗Â<code>~/.yt-dlp/config</code>´╝îňůÂň«×Šś»Šö»ŠîüňĄÜńŞ¬ÚůŹšŻ«ňť░ňŁÇšÜä´╝îŠłĹÚÇëń║ćŔ┐ÖńŞ¬ňť░ňŁÇŃÇé</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#b0c4de;background-color:#282c34;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span style="display:flex;"><span>--proxy 127.0.0.1:8118
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>--cookies-from-browser chrome
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>š╗ÖmpvŔ«żšŻ«yt-dlpšÜäšŤŞňů│ňćůň«╣´╝îňŐáňťĘÚůŹšŻ«Šľçń╗Â<code>~/.config/mpv/mpv.conf</code>ńŞş</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#b0c4de;background-color:#282c34;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic"># Ŕ«żšŻ«yt-dlpšÜäŠľçń╗ÂńŻŹšŻ«</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>script-opts<span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span>ytdl_hook-ytdl_path<span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span>/usr/local/bin/yt-dlp
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic"># Ŕ«żšŻ«Šá╝ň╝Ć´╝îŠłĹŔ┐ÖŔż╣Šś»Intel UHD Graphics 630´╝îŠëÇń╗ąÚÇëŠőęń╝śňůłmp4ňĺîwebm´╝îŠťÇňĄž1080p´╝îš╝ľšáüvp9,hevc,h264,h265Ŕ┐Öń║Ť´╝îňŤáńŞ║av1ńŞŹŠö»ŠîüňĽŐ</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>ytdl-format<span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span><span style="color:#63c381">&#34;(mp4,webm)bestvideo[height&lt;=1080][vcodec~=&#39;^(vp9|(he|a)vc|h26[45])&#39;]+bestaudio/best&#34;</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic"># Ŕ┐ÖŔż╣ÚçŹňĄŹŔ«żšŻ«ńŞÇÚüŹń╗úšÉć</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>ytdl-raw-options-append<span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span><span style="color:#dcaeea">proxy</span><span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span>http://127.0.0.1:8118
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>ŠĺşŠöżšŻĹňŁÇšÜäŠŚÂňÇÖ´╝îŠŐŐ<code>https://</code>ňŹĆŔ««Šö╣ŠłÉ<code>ytdl://</code>´╝îň╝║ňłÂńŻ┐šöĘyt-dlpŠŁąŔžúŠ×ÉŔžćÚóĹňť░ňŁÇŃÇé</p>
<p>ňŽéŠ×ťŔŽüňťĘŠÁĆŔžłňÖĘňĹ╝ŔÁĚmpv´╝îňĆ¬ŔŽüš╗Öxdg-openŠ│Ęňćî<code>ytdl://</code>ňŹĆŔ««´╝îŠľ░ň╗║<code>~/.local/share/applications/ytdl.desktop</code>´╝îňćůň«╣ňŽéńŞő´╝Ü</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#b0c4de;background-color:#282c34;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#c7bf54">[</span>Desktop Entry<span style="color:#c7bf54">]</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#dcaeea">Name</span><span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span>Ytdl Handler
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#dcaeea">Exec</span><span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span>/usr/bin/mpv %u
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#dcaeea">Type</span><span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span>Application
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#dcaeea">MimeType</span><span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span>x-scheme-handler/ytdl;
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>šäÂňÉÄŠëžŔíî<code>update-desktop-database ~/.local/share/applications/</code>ŠŤ┤Šľ░ŠĽ░ŠŹ«ň║ôŃÇé</p>
<p>ŠťÇňÉÄňĆ¬ŔŽüŔ«ęŠÁĆŔžłňÖĘŠëôň╝Ç<code>ytdl://</code>šÜäÚôżŠÄąň░▒ňĆ»ń╗ąń║ćŃÇéŠťÇš«ÇňŹĽŠöÂŔŚĆňĄ╣ŠöżńŞÇńŞ¬jsń╗úšáüŠŁąŠŤ┐ŠŹóŃÇé</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#b0c4de;background-color:#282c34;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#c1abea">javascript</span><span style="color:#c7bf54">:</span>(<span style="color:#c678dd">function</span>() {<span style="color:#ef8383">window</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">location</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">href</span><span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span><span style="color:#ef8383">window</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">location</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">href</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">replace</span>(<span style="color:#56b6c2">/^https?/</span>,<span style="color:#63c381">&#34;ytdl&#34;</span>);})();
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>ŔŽüńŻôÚ¬îŠŤ┤ňąŻňĆ»ń╗ąňćÖŠ▓╣šî┤ŔäÜŠťČšöÜŔç│ŠÁĆŔžłňÖĘŠĆĺń╗ÂŃÇé<br>
ŠÉ×ń║ćńŞÇńŞ¬ňĆ│Úö«ŔÂůÚôżŠÄąŔĆťňŹĽšÜäŠ▓╣šî┤ŔäÜŠťČ´╝îňŽéńŞő</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#b0c4de;background-color:#282c34;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic">// ==UserScript==
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic">// @name Ŕç¬ň«Üń╣ëňĆ│Úö«ŔĆťňŹĽ´╝łŠ▓╣šî┤šëł´╝ë
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic">// @namespace http://tampermonkey.net/
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic">// @version 1.0
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic">// @description ňĆ│Úö«šé╣ňç╗ŔÂůÚôżŠÄąŠŚÂ´╝îŠśżšĄ║Ŕç¬ň«Üń╣ëŔĆťňŹĽ´╝łňĄŹňłÂŃÇüŠëôň╝ÇŃÇüŠľ░ŠáçšşżÚíÁšşë´╝ë
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic">// @author ChatGPT
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic">// @match *://www.youtube.com/*
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic">// @match *://www.bilibili.com/*
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic">// @grant GM_setClipboard
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic">// @run-at document-end
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic">// ==/UserScript==
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic"></span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>(<span style="color:#c678dd">function</span>() {
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> <span style="color:#98c379">&#39;use strict&#39;</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> <span style="color:#c678dd">let</span> <span style="color:#c1abea">customMenu</span> <span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span> <span style="color:#b756ff;font-weight:bold">null</span>; <span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic">// ňşśňéĘŔĆťňŹĽňůâš┤á
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic"></span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> <span style="color:#ef8383">document</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">addEventListener</span>(<span style="color:#63c381">&#34;contextmenu&#34;</span>, <span style="color:#c678dd">function</span>(<span style="color:#c1abea">event</span>) {
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> <span style="color:#c678dd">let</span> <span style="color:#c1abea">target</span> <span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span> <span style="color:#c1abea">event</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">target</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">closest</span>(<span style="color:#63c381">&#34;a&#34;</span>); <span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic">// ňĆ¬ň»╣ŔÂůÚôżŠÄąšöčŠĽł
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic"></span> <span style="color:#c678dd">if</span> (<span style="color:#c7bf54">!</span><span style="color:#c1abea">target</span>) <span style="color:#c678dd">return</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> <span style="color:#c1abea">event</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">preventDefault</span>(); <span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic">// Úś╗ŠşóÚ╗śŔ«ĄňĆ│Úö«ŔĆťňŹĽ
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic"></span> <span style="color:#c1abea">createCustomMenu</span>(<span style="color:#c1abea">target</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">href</span>, <span style="color:#c1abea">event</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">pageX</span>, <span style="color:#c1abea">event</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">pageY</span>);
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> });
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> <span style="color:#c678dd">function</span> <span style="color:#c1abea">createCustomMenu</span>(<span style="color:#c1abea">link</span>, <span style="color:#c1abea">x</span>, <span style="color:#c1abea">y</span>) {
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> <span style="color:#c1abea">removeCustomMenu</span>(); <span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic">// ňůłňłáÚÖĄŠŚžšÜäŔĆťňŹĽ
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic"></span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> <span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic">// ňłŤň╗║ŔĆťňŹĽň«╣ňÖĘ
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic"></span> <span style="color:#c1abea">customMenu</span> <span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span> <span style="color:#ef8383">document</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">createElement</span>(<span style="color:#63c381">&#34;div&#34;</span>);
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> <span style="color:#c1abea">customMenu</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">style</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">position</span> <span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span> <span style="color:#63c381">&#34;absolute&#34;</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> <span style="color:#c1abea">customMenu</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">style</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">top</span> <span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span> <span style="color:#c1abea">y</span> <span style="color:#c7bf54">+</span> <span style="color:#63c381">&#34;px&#34;</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> <span style="color:#c1abea">customMenu</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">style</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">left</span> <span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span> <span style="color:#c1abea">x</span> <span style="color:#c7bf54">+</span> <span style="color:#63c381">&#34;px&#34;</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> <span style="color:#c1abea">customMenu</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">style</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">background</span> <span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span> <span style="color:#63c381">&#34;white&#34;</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> <span style="color:#c1abea">customMenu</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">style</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">border</span> <span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span> <span style="color:#63c381">&#34;1px solid #ccc&#34;</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> <span style="color:#c1abea">customMenu</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">style</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">boxShadow</span> <span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span> <span style="color:#63c381">&#34;2px 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2)&#34;</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> <span style="color:#c1abea">customMenu</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">style</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">padding</span> <span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span> <span style="color:#63c381">&#34;5px 0&#34;</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> <span style="color:#c1abea">customMenu</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">style</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">borderRadius</span> <span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span> <span style="color:#63c381">&#34;5px&#34;</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> <span style="color:#c1abea">customMenu</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">style</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">fontSize</span> <span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span> <span style="color:#63c381">&#34;14px&#34;</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> <span style="color:#c1abea">customMenu</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">style</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">zIndex</span> <span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span> <span style="color:#63c381">&#34;10000&#34;</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> <span style="color:#c1abea">customMenu</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">style</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">cursor</span> <span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span> <span style="color:#63c381">&#34;pointer&#34;</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> <span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic">// ŔĆťňŹĽÚí╣ŠĽ░ŠŹ«
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic"></span> <span style="color:#c678dd">let</span> <span style="color:#c1abea">items</span> <span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span> [
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> { <span style="color:#c1abea">text</span><span style="color:#c7bf54">:</span> <span style="color:#63c381">&#34;ÔľÂ´ŞĆ ńŻ┐šöĘMPVŠĺşŠöż&#34;</span>, <span style="color:#c1abea">action</span><span style="color:#c7bf54">:</span> () =&gt; { <span style="color:#ef8383">window</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">location</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">href</span><span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span><span style="color:#c1abea">link</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">replace</span>(<span style="color:#56b6c2">/^https?/</span>,<span style="color:#63c381">&#34;ytdl&#34;</span>); } },
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> ];
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> <span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic">// ňłŤň╗║ŔĆťňŹĽÚí╣
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic"></span> <span style="color:#c1abea">items</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">forEach</span>(<span style="color:#c1abea">item</span> =&gt; {
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> <span style="color:#c678dd">let</span> <span style="color:#c1abea">menuItem</span> <span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span> <span style="color:#ef8383">document</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">createElement</span>(<span style="color:#63c381">&#34;div&#34;</span>);
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> <span style="color:#c1abea">menuItem</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">textContent</span> <span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span> <span style="color:#c1abea">item</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">text</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> <span style="color:#c1abea">menuItem</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">style</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">padding</span> <span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span> <span style="color:#63c381">&#34;8px 15px&#34;</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> <span style="color:#c1abea">menuItem</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">style</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">whiteSpace</span> <span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span> <span style="color:#63c381">&#34;nowrap&#34;</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> <span style="color:#c1abea">menuItem</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">style</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">color</span> <span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span> <span style="color:#63c381">&#34;#333&#34;</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> <span style="color:#c1abea">menuItem</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">style</span>.<span style="color:#c1abea">background</span> <span style="color:#c7bf54">=</span> <span style="color:#63c381">&#34;white&#34;</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span> <span style="color:#8a93a5;font-style:italic">// ŠéČňüťŠĽłŠ×ť
